00:26:55.720 --> 00:26:58.780
what we're looking for in terms
of figuring out the right time

00:26:58.780 --> 00:27:01.484
to do work during the day
is what social psychologists

00:27:01.484 --> 00:27:02.650
call the "synchrony effect."

00:27:02.650 --> 00:27:05.380
It's sort of a fancy word.

00:27:05.380 --> 00:27:10.495
