back of the envelope way

00:27:46.550 --> 00:27:48.170
to figure out
someone's chronotype.

00:27:48.170 --> 00:27:50.090
So what we're looking for is
the midpoint of your sleep.

00:27:50.090 --> 00:27:51.800
So the midpoint of your sleep--
if you go to sleep at 2:00

00:27:51.800 --> 00:27:54.580
