midpoint of sleep is 6:00 AM.

00:27:57.408 --> 00:27:59.120
And basically the
way it works is

00:27:59.120 --> 00:28:02.840
that if your midpoint
is before 3:30 AM,

00:28:02.840 --> 00:28:05.420
