morning person-- a lark.

00:28:05.420 --> 00:28:11.880
If your midpoint is after 5:30
AM, you're generally an owl.

00:28:11.880 --> 00:28:14.870
So about 15% of us are
larks, 20% of us are owls,

00:28:14.870 --> 00:28:16.754
but 2/3 of us are in the middle.

00:28:16.754 --> 00:28:18.170
And so would you
consider yourself

00:28:18.170 --> 00:28:19.640
